OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772827865
OL,3,CInquiry hears triple killer Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane headbutted and punched police
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FTriple killer Valdo Calocane
OL,8,Fheadbutted, punched and swung
OL,9,Fhandcuffs at a police officer who was
OL,10,Fhelping doctors to detain him two
OL,11,Fyears before he fatally stabbed three
OL,12,Fpeople, the public inquiry into the
OL,13,FNottingham attacks has heard.
OL,15,FCalocane, who was diagnosed with
OL,16,Fparanoid schizophrenia, had been
OL,17,Frefusing to take his medication when
OL,18,Fhe launched an attack on
OL,19,FNottinghamshire Police Constable
OL,20,FBarnaby Pritchard on September 3,
OL,21,F2021, causing swelling to his face.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772827865
OL,3,CInquiry hears triple killer Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane headbutted and punched police
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FThe former student killed University
OL,8,Fof Nottingham undergraduates Barnaby
OL,9,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, both
OL,10,F19, and grandfather Ian Coates, 65,
OL,11,Fand attempted to kill three more
OL,12,Fpeople in the early hours of June 13
OL,13,F2023.
OL,15,FOn Wednesday March 4, PC Pritchard
OL,16,Ftold the inquiry, which is being held
OL,17,Fin London, that he received a call to
OL,18,Fattend Calocane's address in
OL,19,FNottingham, where he was refusing to
OL,20,Fbe be detained by doctors under mental
OL,21,Fhealth laws.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772827865
OL,3,CInquiry hears triple killer Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane headbutted and punched police
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,F"He began just swinging completely out
OL,8,Fof the blue"
OL,10,FCalocane was "very calm" when they
OL,11,Farrived at his address and "was very
OL,12,Funemotional with any response", PC
OL,13,FPritchard said.
OL,15,FThe officer said: "At the time, he
OL,16,Fwasn't demonstrating any warning signs
OL,17,Fthat he could begin assaulting me. As
OL,18,Fsoon as I stepped in the room, he
OL,19,Fbegan just swinging completely out of
OL,20,Fthe blue.
OL,26,@rD@NOUrD@XO]sD@\OUtD@^O]wD@SOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772827865
OL,3,CInquiry hears triple killer Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane headbutted and punched police
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,F"He began punching me repeatedly. As a
OL,8,Fcollective, we managed to restrain him
OL,9,Fagainst an item of furniture inside
OL,10,Fthe room.
OL,12,F"He tried headbutting me, and did
OL,13,Fheadbutt me, while I was trying to
OL,14,Frestrain him."
OL,16,FThe inquiry heard that Calocane swung
OL,17,Fhandcuffs at PC Pritchard "as a
OL,18,Fweapon", but the officer believes he
OL,19,Fmissed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUvD@NO]yD@[OUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772827865
OL,3,CInquiry hears triple killer Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane headbutted and punched police
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FThe officer was left with swelling on
OL,8,Fhis forehead and bruising on his left
OL,9,Fcheek, adding: "I had pain and
OL,10,Fdiscomfort, they were quite sore."
OL,12,FA taser was deployed twice and Pava
OL,13,Fspray, an irritant spray, was used to
OL,14,Frestrain Calocane, the inquiry heard.
OL,26,@qD@POUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
