OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772827865
OL,3,CInquiry hears triple killer Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane headbutted and punched police
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FIn body-worn camera footage played to
OL,8,Fthe inquiry, Calocane can be heard
OL,9,Fsaying when PC Pritchard and three
OL,10,Ffemale officers arrived: "I don't have
OL,11,Fa history of mistreating women",
OL,12,Fbefore saying: "Gentlemen, if you want
OL,13,Fto take me out, I prefer you do it."
OL,15,FAfter his attack on PC Pritchard,
OL,16,FCalocane said: "You didn't go down",
OL,17,Fthe inquiry heard.
OL,26,@rD@ZOUsD@_O]tD@POUuD@dO]xD@POUxD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772827865
OL,3,CInquiry hears triple killer Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane headbutted and punched police
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FAsked by counsel to the inquiry Rachel
OL,8,FLangdale KC what his interpretation of
OL,9,Fthis comment was, PC Pritchard said:
OL,10,F"It was possibly some male bravado `
OL,11,Fhe expected the force of his blows to
OL,12,Fput me to the floor."
OL,14,FIn the footage, Calocane can be heard
OL,15,Fgrunting after being tasered and
OL,16,Fsaying: "No more of that."
OL,18,FReacting to the body-worn footage, Mr
OL,19,FWebber's mother Emma Webber said in a
OL,20,Fstatement:
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@UO]xD@IOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772827865
OL,3,CInquiry hears triple killer Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane headbutted and punched police
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,F"This violent monster is the last face
OL,8,Fmy beautiful son ever saw, and that
OL,9,Fwill haunt me forever. They didn't
OL,10,Fstand a chance, did they."
OL,12,FCalocane was taken in a marked police
OL,13,Fvan to hospital because he had been
OL,14,Ftasered, the inquiry heard, before he
OL,15,Fwas taken to Highbury Hospital, a
OL,16,Fmental health facility.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772827865
OL,3,CInquiry hears triple killer Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane headbutted and punched police
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FHe was later charged with assaulting
OL,8,Fan emergency worker and was summoned
OL,9,Fto attend Nottingham Magistrates'
OL,10,FCourt in September 2022, but he failed
OL,11,Fto appear.
OL,13,FThere was a warrant for his arrest
OL,14,Fwhen he committed the attacks in June
OL,15,F2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1772827865
OL,3,CInquiry hears triple killer Valdo
OL,4,CCalocane headbutted and punched police
OL,5,Cofficer
OL,7,FThe inquiry was previously told that
OL,8,Ftwo months before, Calocane pushed his
OL,9,Fflatmate against the wall, tried to
OL,10,Fget into his locked bedroom during the
OL,11,Fnight, and then stalked him by
OL,12,Ffollowing him home on two occasions.
OL,14,FThese incidents were reported to the
OL,15,Fpolice, but no further action was
OL,16,Ftaken against Calocane, the inquiry
OL,17,Fheard.
OL,19,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/10
